@startuml REQ-0012 Sensor Calibration
autonumber

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Sensor Driver" as Sensor_Driver
end box

header
  **REQ-0012: Sensor Calibration**
  //Description:// Apply factory calibration offsets using controller data
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Sensor_Calibrate retrieves and applies offsets from Controller_GetCalibration
end header

note over Sensor_Driver: Sensor_Calibrate()

Sensor_Driver -> Sensor_Driver: Controller_GetCalibration()

@enduml